reviewText: My Granddaughter was thrilled with this movie.  The old one she had got broken.  Thank you!

I had all the Disney sing-along tapes when my son was little. He loved them and sang along with them. Then one day my mother gave them away to her girlfriends kids which made me very upset. Now I am trying to replace them for my two little granddaughters. I ordered the sing along songs, the early years at it came sooner than I expected and I am very pleased. I hope to have all of them before the end of the year. Thank you Karin
Just as described! Brand new. Packed well!
We got the tape which plays good, our kids are happy.. even it was old one! This is very good for kids watch & learn too! Thank you & have a nice day!
Wish these were available on DVD.  These three older collections are the best of Disney Classics!!!
